### Question 3: "Will the market reverse?"

Reversals are detected by **divergences** between signals:

| Divergence Pattern | What It Means | Data Sources |
|-------------------|---------------|-------------|
| **DP accumulating BUT price dropping** | Smart money buying into weakness = bottom forming | DP trend vs SPY price |
| **DP distributing BUT price rising** | Smart money selling into strength = top forming | DP trend vs SPY price |
| **Signals bullish BUT VIX spiking (Tier 3+)** | Volatility crush incoming â€” signals may be stale | Signals vs VIX regime |
| **Call wall moving DOWN across expirations** | Dealers unwinding upside protection = ceiling dropping | Multi-date option walls |
| **Put wall moving UP across expirations** | Dealers building downside protection = floor rising | Multi-date option walls |
| **Short volume % surging > 65%** | Heavy short selling â€” could be covering catalyst | Short volume trend |
| **Tactical shifting from risk to defensive** | Model flipping to gold/commodities from equities | Tactical positions |

**Reversal detection today:**
